[The approach adopted in Texas -- testing the dog for the virus and monitoring for possible infection -- seems sensible. The veterinarians treating and caring for Bentley have said he is the perfect patient -- easy to care for and very responsive to them. It is delightful to know both Ms Pham and Bentley will soon be healthy and reunited. - Mod.TG

